{"body": "A tax (to be known as \u201c\"land transaction tax\u201d\u201d) is to be charged on land transactions.\nThe tax is chargeable\u2014\nwhether or not there is an instrument effecting the transaction,\nif there is such an instrument, regardless of where it is executed, and\nregardless of where any party to the transaction is or is resident.\nThe Welsh Revenue Authority (\u201c\u201cWRA\u201d\u201d) is to be responsible for the collection and management of the tax.", "citation_label": "ANAW 2017/1 s. 2", "citation_path": "uk/statute/anaw/2017/1/2", "document_class": "statute", "expression_date": "2026-06-07", "heading": "Section 2", "id": "c0ed96f3-687b-5080-9c87-876bfd13213e", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "1", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "2", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "anaw", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2017"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "section", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "ANAW 2017/1 s. 2", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["E", "W"], "references_to": ["anaw/2017/1"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 2, "parent_citation_path": "uk/statute/anaw/2017/1", "parent_id": "a21919c0-15ae-5c8b-8b07-e9111cdabe0e", "source_as_of": "2026-06-07", "source_document_id": "anaw/2017/1", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/anaw/2017/1/section/2", "source_path": "sources/uk/statute/2026-06-07-uk-ltt-act-section-2/anaw/2017/1/section-2.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/anaw/2017/1/section/2", "version": "2026-06-07-uk-ltt-act-section-2"}
